## v2.0.0 — 2026-06-13 (verified-ci)

Promoted to verified-ci after PR #1307 merged to ProjectHephaestus (4058 passed, 85.57% coverage).

Key changes from v1.0.0:
- Fixed critical assertion bug: `== inner` → `== inner.resolve()` throughout Quick Reference and all code examples
- Added "Critical Insight: resolve() Symmetry" section explaining why `.resolve()` is required on both sides
- Expanded Failed Attempts table with 3 additional entries (no-resolve, git-init, copy-existing-style, parametrize)
- Added verified-ci outcome and PR/Issue links
- Tags expanded: added path-resolution, innermost-wins, first-match-up, symlink, resolve
- Description updated to include symlinked-tmpdir CI environments as an explicit use-case trigger
- Seed depth recommendation strengthened to 2 levels below inner (not just 1)
- Added Step 7 (run full test class) to Detailed Steps
